                     <interp inst="t18320906-273-person2236" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am warden of the Inner Temple. I have seen the two prisoners go through at various times; I saw them together about June and July, and sometimes apart - I remember Mr. Maltby's chambers being robbed; I had seen them lately before that.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320906-273-person2237">
