                     <interp inst="t18320906-273-person2244" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Maria lodged at my house for some time; she had no watch when she first came, but I afterwards saw a silver watch in her bed-room; Austin was in the<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183209060119"></xptr>habit of coming there backwards and forwards - they left the latter end of June.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320906-273-person2245">
